headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Jabil After Its 52% Surge In 2025?
summary: If you are wondering whether Jabil’s huge run means you have already missed the boat or if there is still real value left in the tank, this breakdown is for you. Despite a choppy week with the share price down 7.4%, Jabil is still up 9.1% over the last month, 51.9% year to date, and 415.6% over 5 years. This indicates that the market has been steadily upgrading its view of the business. Recent headlines have focused on Jabil’s ongoing portfolio reshaping, including divesting lower margin...
